<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="26" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,152,551]" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,323,413,439]" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[332,547,413,438]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Systropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oestrus">
<emphasis box="[332,547,413,438]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">Systropus oestrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was established by 
<bibRefCitation author="Du" box="[797,1049,413,439]" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" refString="Yao, G., Du, J. P., Yang, C. K., Cui, W. N. &amp; Yang, D. (2009) Bombyliidae. In: Yang, D. [Ed.], Fauna of Hebei (Diptera). China Agricultural Science and Technology Press, Beijing, pp. 312 - 324." type="book chapter" year="2009">
Du and Yang (
<number box="[975,1040,413,439]" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" value="2009.0">2009</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
according to one male and one female specimens. After examination and comparison of the 
<typeStatus box="[894,946,450,476]" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">type</typeStatus>
series of 
<taxonomicName box="[1067,1185,450,475]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Systropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oestrus">
<emphasis box="[1067,1185,450,475]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">S. oestrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1246,1390,450,475]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Systropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chinensis">
<emphasis box="[1246,1390,450,475]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">S. chinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, no distinct differences from 
<taxonomicName box="[447,586,488,513]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Systropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chinensis">
<emphasis box="[447,586,488,513]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">S. chinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were found. Consequently, 
<taxonomicName box="[916,1029,488,513]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Systropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oestrus">
<emphasis box="[916,1029,488,513]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">S. oestrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is undoubtedly a new synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[151,289,525,550]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Systropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chinensis">
<emphasis box="[151,289,525,550]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="26">S. chinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
